{"tid":1117561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拔菜總部行動劇「炸平總統府」","createTime":"2019-04-20T18:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T18:11:48.000Z","uid":40108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cb7727cde428ed4f6c916b5065d5634c2b0860","tid":1117561,"uid":40108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:11:37.000Z","msg":"片: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ETtodaySHARE/videos/762741684126871/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FETtodaySHARE%2Fvideos%2F762741684126871%2F&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=41955353\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ETtodaySHARE/videos/762741684126871/</a><br />\n<br />\n記者蔣婕妤／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n總統府6日晚間舉辦總統府音樂會，反蔡政府臉書社團「全民拔菜總部」晚間5點在中正紀念堂搶先舉辦「死亡音樂會」抗議總統蔡英文，現場上演象徵性「炸平總統府」行動劇，不過，主辦單位雖然在3日前於臉書邀請支持者踴躍參與，現場卻不見支持者到場力挺。<br />\n<br />\n「全民拔菜總部」臉書社團貼文指出，「6日下午五時請大家到中正紀念堂大門來參加拔菜總部的好戲，總督府百年死亡音樂會。蔡英文媚日集團在慶祝總督府建立100年，在凱道舉辦慶祝音樂會。總司令要用最精彩的倒退嚕幫她門做法事牽亡過橋。請大家踴躍出席和台奸獨孬孬們拼場。」<br />\n<br />\n拔菜總部3日在臉書發文邀請支持者踴躍出席，不過整場抗議只有主辦單位，不見支持者。拔菜總部下午5點鐘準時開始抗議行動，現場擺出總統府看版，還有兩顆「炸彈」，透過「自備音效」上演炸平總統府戲碼。主辦單位頻頻高喊「我要做一個堂堂正正的中國人」，他們強調，不滿蔡政府盛大替日本人建立的總統府辦音樂會，要把不滿的聲音大聲說出來。<br />\n<br />\n面對抗議團體，張惇涵回應，總統府音樂會在籌備階段時，國安單位已經有注意到維安問題，由於總統府音樂會活動是開放民眾自由入場，還是會以給民眾方便為主，針對陳抗團體，警方會依造標準作業程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190406/1416536.htm?from=fb_et_share_video&amp;fbclid=IwAR3ueaAp6TktdRBd0QjqMCGWcJSX5Z7uWe4-mr9nT0W9iH-zlCTLSy4CD5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190406%2F1416536.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_share_video%26fbclid%3DIwAR3ueaAp6TktdRBd0QjqMCGWcJSX5Z7uWe4-mr9nT0W9iH-zlCTLSy4CD5E&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=89280132\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190406/1416536.htm?from=fb_et_share_video&amp;fbclid=IwAR3ueaAp6TktdRBd0QjqMCGWcJSX5Z7uWe4-mr9nT0W9iH-zlCTLSy4CD5E</a>"},{"pid":"3b5dc2abdac1aed27c1ccba78f83e071ab1ab18c","tid":1117561,"uid":40108,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"3..2..1... 發射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實在是太準了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不但命中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且還命中正紅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><